The document alleges that Ronaldo confirmed that he had had sexual relations with the accuser, but that they were consensual.
Mayorga claims to have addressed the police and photographs of her injuries were taken at the hospital, but later accepted a settlement outside the courtroom because she was “scared of the possibility of revenge” and was concerned that “she would be publicly humiliated.”
